{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"b094b35d8a","title":"“河南农学院是上饶集中营还是高等学校？”","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ac54dcf6ff","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"b094b35d8a"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"0dff85fda0","name":"卢炳忠"},{"id":"27c4c4fb2e","name":"郭章学"},{"id":"6c72d91291","name":"河南农学院"},{"id":"bcd33ba6ce","name":"唐厥旺"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"3de0f72274","type":"title","text":"“河南农学院是上饶集中营还是高等学校？”","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b094b35d8a"},{"id":"3b0b0758cc","type":"authors","text":"河南农学院卢炳忠郭章学唐厥旺","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b094b35d8a"},{"id":"f32de0e0df","type":"paragraph","text":"卢炳忠（农60级学生）：在肃反运动中，当时的禹王台，在古柏的衬托下，显得那样的阴森，猫头鹰也在叫，到处是棍棒声和呻吟声，吓人极了，真像一座集中营。我真不知道他们（注：指党员干部）是共产党员还是国民党员，河南农学院是上饶集中营还是高等学校？","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b094b35d8a"},{"id":"a680b3a105","type":"paragraph","text":"郭章学（农59级学生）：在肃反运动中产生的违法乱纪现象，我院领导上是明知故犯。肃反对象受尽了各种折磨。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b094b35d8a"},{"id":"766dd3c3b6","type":"paragraph","text":"我院是班房，是监狱。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b094b35d8a"},{"id":"f68d83fe9e","type":"paragraph","text":"唐厥旺（理化教研组助教）：肃反中的积极分子连国民党都不如，和中美合作所（注：蒋美合办的特务机关）一样。党委书记是杀人犯，共产党员连起码的人道主义都没有。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b094b35d8a"},{"id":"3fbadaac96","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《右派言论选辑》（河南农学院，1957年12月）。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b094b35d8a"}],"page":{"id":"d084fb3683","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b094b35d8a","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}